description: Find a company authorised for handling wood and material affected by Ips typographus or Phytophthora pluvialis.

details.body:
There are limitations on the handling of material infected with Ips typographus or Phytophthora pluvialis.

Infected material can only be moved to a processer authorised to receive and process that infected material.

Ips typographus authorised processers

There are differing risk categories of this material. You must ensure that the business is authorised to receive the appropriate category of material from your site. Check the last column ‘material status’ in the table to identify each processors’ material authorisation.

For more information, or if you have difficulty reaching any of these businesses contact Plant Health Forestry Ips typographus authorisation team.
